      • updateCapk

        public void updateCapk(CAPK capk)
        update a Certificate Authority Public Key object for contact config.

        Callback :
        ConfigurationController.ConfigurationDelegate.onCapkUpdated(boolean)

        Parameters:
        capk - The CAPK object to be updated.

        The object contains the location of the CAPK in the device, the RID, index, modulus, exponent and the checksum of the CAPK, all data in hex string format.

      • updateAid

        public void updateAid(java.util.Hashtable<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> data)
        update the AID info for contact config.
        To add new AID, calls getAidInfo to locate an appIndex with AID 16 bytes 0xFF, then call updateAid to update its info.
        To remove an App, set AID value to 16 bytes 0xFF.
        The online config form will not in sync with firmware config after modifying the AID info with updateAid command.

        Callback :
        ConfigurationController.ConfigurationDelegate.onAidUpdated(Hashtable)

        Parameters:
        data - hashtable key and value

      • updateAid

        public void updateAid(boolean aFlagCl,
                      java.util.Hashtable<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> data)
        update the AID info.
        To add new AID, calls getAidInfo to locate an appIndex with AID 16 bytes 0xFF, then call updateAid to update its info.
        To remove an App, set AID value to 16 bytes 0xFF.
        The online config form will not in sync with firmware config after modifying the AID info with updateAid command.

        Callback :
        ConfigurationController.ConfigurationDelegate.onAidUpdated(Hashtable)

        Parameters:
        aFlagCl - true: Contactless Config, false contact Config
        data - hashtable key and value

        KEY_ACTION : Upadate options - ACTION_UPDATE, ACTION_REMOVE.
        KEY_AID : Tag 9F06 data.
        KEY_APPVERSION : Tag 9F09 data.
        KEY_CONTACTTACDEFAULT : TAC DEFAULT for Contact Kernel
        KEY_CONTACTTACDENIAL : TAC DENIAL for Contact Kernel
        KEY_CONTACTTACONLINE : TAC ONLINE for Contact Kerne
        KEY_CONTACTLESSTACDEFAULT : TAC DEFAULT for Contactless Kernel.
        KEY_CONTACTLESSTACDENIAL : TAC DENIAL for Contactless Kernel.
        KEY_CONTACTLESSTACONLINE : TAC ONLINE for Contactless Kernel.
        KEY_DEFAULTTDOL : Tag 97 data.
        KEY_DEFAULTDDOL : Tag 9F49 data.
        KEY_CONTACTLESSTRANSACTIONLIMIT : Contactless Transaction Limit.
        KEY_CONTACTLESSTRANSACTIONLIMITODCV : Contactless ODCVM Limit.
        KEY_CONTACTLESSCVMREQUIREDLIMIT : Contactless CVM Limit.
        KEY_CONTACTLESSFLOORLIMIT : Contactless Floor Limit
        KEY_TERMINALFLOORLIMIT : Tag 9F1B data.
        KEY_TERMINALCAPABILITIES : Tag 9F33 data.
        KEY_ADDITTERMCAPABILITIES : Tag 9F40 data.
        KEY_OVERSEAFLOORLIMIT : Tag DF7F data.
        KEY_TERMINALCOUNTRYCODE : Tag 9F1A data.
        KEY_TERMINALRISKMGMDATA : Tag 9F1D data.
        KEY_TRANSCURRENCYCODE : Tag 5F2A data.
        KEY_CLT_COMBINATION_OPTIONS : JCB Combination Options.
        KEY_CLT_KERNEL_INFO : Contactless Kernel Info.
        KEY_ETYPE : EMV Kernel Type
        KEY_EBITFIELD : Kernel Config configuration bit.
        KEY_ERSBTHRESH : Threshold for biased random selection.
        KEY_ERSTARGET : Target for random selection.
        KEY_ERSBMAX : Maxminum target for biased random selection.
        KEY_TERMINALTYPE : Tag 9F35 data.
        KEY_TID : Tag 9F1C data.
        KEY_XP_TERM_CAP : Tag 9F6D data.
        KEY_XP_TXN_CAP : Tag 9F6E data.
        KEY_TTQORPUNATC : Default Tag 9F66 data.
        KEY_TRANSACTIONTYPE : Tag 9C data.
        KEY_PWAVEENCHANCEDDDAIDR : Tag DF03 data.
        KEY_PWAVECVMREQUIREMENT : Tag DF04 data.
        KEY_PWAVEDISPOFFLFUNDIDR : Tag DF05 data.
        KEY_CLTTERMENTRYCAP : Tag DFBF data.
        KEY_CLTVFLAG : Tag DFBE data.
        KEY_CLTPPINFLAG : Tag DFA5 data.
        KEY_ACQUIRERIDENTIFIER : Tag 9F01 data.
        KEY_TRANSCURRENCYEXPONENT : Tag 5F36 data.
        KEY_MERCHANTNAMEANDLOCATION : Tag 9F4E data.
        KEY_MERCHANTCATCODE : Tag 9F15 data.
        KEY_MERCHANTIDENTIFIER : Tag 9F16 data
        KEY_MC_CVMCAP_CVMREQ : MC CVM Capability - CVM Req
        KEY_MC_CVMCAP_NOCVMREQ : MC CVM Capability - NO CVM Req
        KEY_MC_KERNEL_CFG : MC Kernel Cfg
        KEY_MC_SECURITY_CAP : MC Security Cap.
        KEY_MCTCC_JSTIP : Tag 9F53 data.
